quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  52,32,Em teÂṀmuruhum ahlamuhum bihaza em hum kavmun taÄun
  52,33,Em yekulune tekavveleh bel la yuÂṀminun
  52,34,FelyeÂṀtu bi hadisim mislihi in kanu sadikÄḟyn
  52,35,Em huliku min Äayri ÅeyÂṀin em humul halikun
  52,36,Em halekus semavati vel ard bel la yukÄḟnun
  52,37,Em Äḟndehum hazainu rabbike em humul musaytÄḟrun
  52,38,Em lehum sullemuy yestemiune fih felyeti mustemiuhum bi sultanim mubin
  52,39,Em lehul benatu ve lekumul benun
  52,40,Em tesÂṀeluhum ecran fe hum mim maÄramim muskalun
  52,41,Em Äḟndehumul Äaybu fe hum yektubun
  52,42,Em yuridune keyda fellezine keferu humul mekidun
  52,43,Em lehum ilahun Äayrullah subhanellahi amma yuÅrikun
  52,44,Ve iy yerav kisfem mines semai sakÄḟtay yekulu sehabum merkum
  52,45,Fe zerhum hatta yulaku yevmehumullezi fihi yusÂṀakun
  52,46,Yevme la yuÄni anhum keyduhum ÅeyÂṀev ve la hum yunsarun
  52,47,Ve inne fillezine zalemu azaben dune zalike ve lakinne ekserahum la yaÂṀlemun
  52,48,Vasbir li hukmi rabbike fe inneke bi aÂṀyunina ve sebbÄḟh bi hamdi rabbike hÄḟyne tekum
  52,49,Ve minel leyli fesebbÄḟhhu ve idbaran nucum